name: 1010 complex lines 3/10
description:
This is edition #3 of the physical generative art series titled "1010 complex lines". 

Each of the 10 editions consists of 10 of the most complex lines (according to Claude Shannon's entropy theorem) from my database of recorded cursor lines.

Artist: Marcel Schwittlick (@schwittlick_)
Technique: Industrial wax on 190gsm Hahnemühle paper
Dimensions: DIN A1 (59,4 x 84,1cm / 23,4 x 33,1in)
Edition: 1/1
Date: 07.01.2021

The NFT comes with the original drawing, international shipping included. Upon resale on the secondary market the original drawing shall be sent to the new owner. Shipping will be covered by the new owner.
